@startuml
actor Penjual
boundary View
control ProductController
entity ProductModel
entity VariantModel
database Database

Penjual -> View: Buka Menu Tambah Produk
Penjual -> View: Isi Form & Varian & Upload Gambar (Submit)
View -> ProductController: POST /seller/products

ProductController -> ProductController: Validasi Request Data
alt Data Valid?
    ProductController -> ProductModel: addProduct(product_data)
    ProductModel -> Database: INSERT products
    Database --> ProductModel: OK (product_id)
    
    loop Untuk Setiap Varian
        ProductController -> VariantModel: create(variant_data + product_id)
        VariantModel -> Database: INSERT variants
    end
    
    ProductController -> ProductController: Store Image to Storage
    ProductController --> View: Redirect dengan Pesan Sukses
else Data Tidak Valid
    ProductController --> View: Redirect Back with Errors
end
View --> Penjual: Tampilkan Halaman Daftar Produk
@enduml